  "url": "https://www.nps.gov/grca/planyourvisit/lost-found.htm",
  "title": "Lost & Found Property - Grand Canyon National Park (U.S. National Park Service)",
  "html": "<body class=\"ParkSite\"><span aria-label=\"Top of page\" id=\"__topdoc__\" role=\"navigation\"></span>\n\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n<div id=\"beforeSkipLinks\" tabindex=\"-1\"></div>\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n<div class=\"GlobalHeader usaGlobalHeader\" role=\"banner\">\n\n</div>\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<div aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-labelledby=\"exitModalLabel\" class=\"modal refreshableModal\" id=\"myModal\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"modal-dialog\">\n<div class=\"modal-content\">\n<div class=\"modal-header\">\n<h2 class=\"modal-title visually-hidden\" id=\"exitModalLabel\">Exiting nps.gov</h2>\n<button aria-label=\"Close\" class=\"btn-close\" data-bs-dismiss=\"modal\" type=\"button\"></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"modal-body\"></div>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Schedule\" id=\"cs_control_481716\"><div id=\"CS_Element_BannerContainer\" title=\"\"><div class=\"cs_GridRow\" id=\"gridRow_1_1_481716\"><div class=\"cs_GridColumn\" id=\"gridCol_1_1_1_1_481716\"><div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_CustomCF\" id=\"cs_control_830326\"><div id=\"CS_CCF_1918496_830326\">\n\n</div></div><div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_CustomCF\" id=\"cs_control_481855\"><div id=\"CS_CCF_1918496_481855\"> </div></div></div></div></div></div>\n<div id=\"Park-header\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"pull-left\">\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n\n</div>\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div aria-label=\"Alerts Notification\" class=\"AlertsNotification\" data-site-code=\"grca\" id=\"AlertsNotification\" role=\"dialog\">\n<div aria-live=\"polite\" class=\"AlertsNotification__Status visually-hidden\" role=\"status\">Loading alerts</div>\n<div class=\"collapse\">\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__Panel\">\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__Header\">\n<h2 class=\"Tag\" id=\"AlertsNotificationHeading\">Alerts In Effect</h2>\n<button aria-label=\"Dismiss\" class=\"AlertsNotification__DismissButton\" type=\"button\">\nDismiss\n<svg class=\"usa-icon\" focusable=\"false\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use href=\"/theme/assets/vendor/npsds/packages/icons/dist/sprite.svg#close\"></use>\n</svg>\n</button>\n<span class=\"hr clearfix\"></span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__Body\" id=\"AlertsNotificationBody\">\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__MoreLinkContainer\">\n<svg class=\"usa-icon\" focusable=\"false\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use href=\"/theme/assets/vendor/npsds/packages/icons/dist/sprite.svg#add\"></use>\n</svg>\n<a class=\"AlertsNotification__MoreLink\" href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/conditions.htm\" id=\"AlertsNotificationMoreLink\" tabindex=\"-1\">\nmore information on current conditions...\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"MainContent\" id=\"main\" role=\"main\">\n\n<div aria-labelledby=\"modal-contact-us-label\" class=\"modal fade\" id=\"modal-contact-us\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"modal-dialog\">\n<div class=\"modal-content\">\n<div class=\"modal-header\">\n<h4 class=\"modal-title visually-hidden\" id=\"modal-contact-us-label\">Contact Us</h4>\n<button aria-label=\"Close\" class=\"btn-close\" data-bs-dismiss=\"modal\" type=\"button\"></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"modal-body\">\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"adminTools\"></div>\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"ColumnGrid row\">\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n<div class=\"container\">\n\n</div>\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<div class=\"ColumnMain col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"ContentHeader text-content-size\">\n<h1 class=\"page-title\">Lost &amp; Found Property</h1>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Layout\" id=\"cs_control_2\"><table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"CS_Layout_Table\" id=\"cs_idLayout2\" summary=\"\" width=\"100%\"><tr class=\"CS_Layout_TR\"><td class=\"CS_Layout_TD\" id=\"cs_idCell2x1x1\">\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_1918498\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<p>If you are in Grand Canyon National Park and have<strong> lost an item</strong>, there are several places your item(s) could be.<br/>\n<br/>\nIf you have <strong>found an item </strong>please take it to the park location nearest you.</p>\n<h3>South Rim</h3>\n<p><strong>South Rim Visitor Center (National Park Service)</strong><br/>\nGeneral locations throughout the park, scenic overlooks, etc.<br/>\n<a href=\"/common/utilities/sendmail/sendemail.cfm?o=4C97D8BAA2DFA0AF808412A1FD28ADA2539342AF52A69FD15810B8&amp;r=/grca/planyourvisit/lost-found.htm\" id=\"/common/utilities/sendmail/sendemail.cfm?o=4C97D8BAA2DFA0AF808412A1FD28ADA2539342AF52A69FD15810B8&amp;r=/grca/planyourvisit/lost-found.htm|\">e-mail us</a><br/>\n928-638-7798<br/>\n<br/>\n<strong>Xanterra Parks and Resorts</strong><br/>\nEl Tovar Hotel, Bright Angel Lodge, Thunderbird Lodge, Kachina Lodge, Maswik Lodge, Hermits Rest, Phantom Ranch.<br/>\n<a href=\"/common/utilities/sendmail/sendemail.cfm?o=4C86C8A991DCBCA8B4A312A1ED12B9BF47D3458051&amp;r=/grca/planyourvisit/lost-found.htm\" id=\"/common/utilities/sendmail/sendemail.cfm?o=4C86C8A991DCBCA8B4A312A1ED12B9BF47D3458051&amp;r=/grca/planyourvisit/lost-found.htm|\">gcsrlost@xanterra.com</a><br/>\n928-638-2526 ext. 6503<br/>\n<br/>\n<strong>Delaware North Parks and Resorts</strong><br/>\nYavapai Lodge, Trailer Village RV Park, Canyon Village Market/Deli, Desert View Trading Post/Deli/General Store. <br/>\n<a href=\"/common/utilities/sendmail/sendemail.cfm?o=4686D3BA8EC7AEB5B4BF16A3F800AABF4393499D48BEC29C5012&amp;r=/grca/planyourvisit/lost-found.htm\" id=\"/common/utilities/sendmail/sendemail.cfm?o=4686D3BA8EC7AEB5B4BF16A3F800AABF4393499D48BEC29C5012&amp;r=/grca/planyourvisit/lost-found.htm|\">mchastai@delawarenorth.com</a><br/>\n928-638-4001 (For items lost or found in Yavapai lodge, restaurant or retail outlet.) Please take found items to any Delaware North operated facility.</p>\n<h3>North Rim</h3>\n<p><strong><em><a href=\"/grca/northrimstatus.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=8060425,northrimstatus.htm,10957|\">North Rim - Current Status and Closures</a></em></strong><br/>\n<br/>\n<strong>If you are no longer in the park, you are invited to make a lost property report and send it to Grand Canyon National Park's Lost and Found Office. Please include the following information:</strong></p>\n<ul type=\"disc\">\n<li>name</li>\n<li>mailing address</li>\n<li>telephone number</li>\n<li>item lost</li>\n<li>description of item lost with name of manufacturer, model number, color, and any specifics that will help us identify your property</li>\n<li>date lost</li>\n<li>where you believe the item was lost</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Email</strong> this information to <a href=\"/common/utilities/sendmail/sendemail.cfm?o=6CB7F89AA2FFA0AF808412A1FD288DA2539342AF52A69FD15810B8&amp;r=/grca/planyourvisit/lost-found.htm\" id=\"/common/utilities/sendmail/sendemail.cfm?o=6CB7F89AA2FFA0AF808412A1FD288DA2539342AF52A69FD15810B8&amp;r=/grca/planyourvisit/lost-found.htm|\">e-mail us</a>.</p>\n<p>Or, if you wish to leave a report in person, call the Grand Canyon National Park Lost and Found Office at <strong>(928) 638-7798</strong>. If the answering machine picks up, please press #1 and leave a message about your lost property.<br/>\n</p>\n<p>Or <strong>write us at:</strong> Lost and Found Office, Grand Canyon National Park, P.O. Box 129, Grand Canyon, AZ, 86023.</p>\n</div></div>\n</td></tr>\n</table></div>\n</div><!-- col-sm-12 -->\n</div><!-- row -->\n</div><!-- ColumnMain col-sm-9 -->\n</div><!-- ColumnGrid row -->\n</div><!-- end container -->\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"ColumnGrid row\">\n<div class=\"ColumnMain col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-12 text-content-size text-content-style\">\n<p style=\"text-align:right;\">Last updated: September 25, 2025</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n <!-- ParkFooter -->\n<!--googleon: index-->\n\n</div><!-- end of <div main> -->\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<!-- the rest of the scripts are leftovers from before the centennial down and should be pared down where possible -->\n\n<link href=\"/common/commonspot/templates/assets/libs/colorbox/colorbox.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n\n<div class=\"modal fade\" id=\"outdated-browser\" role=\"dialog\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n</div>\n</body>",
